{"id": "pos033", "name": "Cam_ARC_H_694_04_30", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "Network bridge activate, 88%... 89%...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher E"], "content": "Interface synchronization complete, prepare to connect.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Begin virtual connection.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher U"], "content": "Begin virtual connection.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Please... please succeed...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "Virtual connection... success! Thank goodness!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Alright! I knew we could do it!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher U"], "content": "Begin formatting the memory of the \"vessel\".\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Director, I really appreciate your help.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>... I'm very interested in this project of yours too. Been a few years since we last met. You've become more like a director than I ever was.</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I still got much to learn... like what I'm doing now. It's all for the trivial goal of saving a family member. Compare to your grand aspirations...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Aspirations, eh... I've done way too many despicable and brutal things in order to achieve those. \"Appearance Cloning\"... such a disgraceful technology, yet it was just one of the many dirty tricks I used to climb to the top.\nI had sealed this away for good...</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I had to ask so many time before you finally agree to help. You have my sincere gratitude...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Your resolve to save her somewhat resonated with me. However, keep this in mind. What you have here was obtained by sacrificing an innocent life. Its price...</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes... I know.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>You... have truly changed.</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\nNevertheless... This girl, she really does look exactly the same... With your support, the transformation really removed every single trace of her previous appearance.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Your wife... will she accept this?</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "She will accept it, and I will succeed.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Does having someone's appearance and memory make you \"that\" person?\nIt really is fragile, isn't it? What we humans consider our basis of existence...</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>However, this is also precisely why it's so precious. The fact that you're willing to break this moral framework for science shows that you've grown quite a bit yourself too.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... I'm... I'm not what director described, in fact far from it.\nAroma... she's someone I truly treasured, yet I did that to her...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Regardless of what sins you believe you committed, what you're doing now, working so hard to let her live, is perhaps the only way for you to atone for your sins</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "The only way for me to atone for my sins... is it?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>Yes, even if you can't receive forgiveness, you still do it.</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "It feels like... director, you've changed as well.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>... Maybe it's because I also have someone I care greatly about now, just like you.</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Yes, I care greatly about her... and I care greatly about this family. I don't want to see anyone in grief anymore.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "Memory formatting complete. Director! Everything is going smoothly so far!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>These images... Are they the original memory of this girl?</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes. In this stage, we'll be formatting the memory of the vessel.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>She was a very beautiful girl.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Yes, she was. But... sorry.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteMemories_UI", "Memory delete"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher U"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Researcher E"], "content": "... This feels... a lot heavier than I imagined...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>From now on, it'll be your time to shine. Go, save her.</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... this is going to hurt a bit. Please, bear with it...\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "ブリッジ起動。88%……89%……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "同期完了。接続準備。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "神経接続開始。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "神経接続開始。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "頼む……成功してくれ……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "神経接続……成功です！やりました！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "よし！\n問題ないと分かっていた！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "「容器」の記憶をフォーマット化します。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "チーフ、お力を貸していただきありがとうございました。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……私も、お前の研究に興味がある。\n数年会わない間に、当時の私よりよほどチーフらしくなったみたいだな。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "まだまだですよ……\n今も、ただ家族を救いたい、それだけですから。\nあなたの理想と比べれば……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>理想か……\n私はこれまで残忍で人としてあるまじき行為を重ねてきてしまった。\n上へ上へと上り詰めるために、手段を選ばずなんでもやった。\n封印したはずの……</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "何度も頼み込んで、ようやく答えてもらうことができました。\n本当に感謝しています……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>お前の彼女を救いたいという気持ちが、私にも分かる部分があってね。\nだが、覚えておくんだ。\nこれは、一つの命を犠牲にして手に入れたものだ。その対価は……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "はい……分かっています。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>お前は……本当に変わったな。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\nですが……本当にまったく一緒ですね。\nこの女の子は……あなたのお力添えのもと改造され、今では元の面影は全く残っていない。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>君の奥さんは……それでいいのか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "彼女も分かってくれるはずです。\n必ず成功させます。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>その人の姿かたちと記憶があれば、その人に成り代わることができるのか？\n人類の存在の根拠は実に儚い……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>だが、だからこそ大切なものだ。\n科学のために道徳を捨てたお前は、成長した。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……自分は……主任の言うほど偉大ではありません。\nAromaちゃんのことを大切にしたいと……そう思っているのに、あんなことを……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>君が彼女に何をしたのか、何に対して罪の意識を感じているのかは分からないが、彼女を生かしてあげることも、彼女に対する唯一の贖罪方法なのではないか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "唯一の贖罪方法……？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>そうだ。\nたとえ許されなくても、やるしかない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "チーフ……変わりましたね。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……私も、大切にしたい人ができたのだよ。\n君のようにな。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そうなんです……僕は……彼女が大事で……この家族が大事で……もう誰かが傷つくところを見たくはない。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "記憶のフォーマット化終了。\nチーフ！順調です！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>これは……この少女の記憶か？</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "はい。\n今は容器の記憶をフォーマット化しています。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>美しい子だ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ですね。\nこの子には申し訳なりませんが……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteMemories_UI", "記憶を消す"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "……思っていたより……重いな……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>ここからはお前の力を発揮する時だ。\nさあ、助けてやるんだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aromaちゃん……少し痛いだろうけど……我慢してね……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "橋接器啟動，88%……89%……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "界面同步完成，準備連線。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "開始精神連線。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "開始精神連線。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜託了……一定要成功……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "精神連線……成功！太好了！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好！我就知道一定沒問題！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "開始格式化「容器」記憶。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "主任，很感謝你的幫忙。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我對你的這個項目也很感興趣。幾年沒見，你真的變得比我還有主任的樣子了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我還差得遠呢……像現在這樣，也只是為了拯救自己的親人，跟你的理想比起來……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>理想……我做過太多傷天害理的事。「複製容貌」這種骯髒的技術，也是為了往上爬而不擇手段。原本已經被我封印了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜託你好多次，總算是答應了，真的很謝謝你……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你想拯救她的執著，讓我稍微有點共鳴了。不過記住了，這可是在犧牲了一條無辜的生命之下換來的，它的代價……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……我知道。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你……真的變了啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n但……還真的是一模一樣，這個女孩……在你的支援下被改造後，根本看不出她原本的樣子。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你老婆……會接受嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她會接受的，我會成功的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>有了一個人的容貌與記憶後，就能成為他嗎？人類的存在依據真的非常脆弱啊……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>但也正因如此才顯得珍貴。能為科學打破道德框架的你，也成長了不少。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……沒有主任說得那麼偉大。Aroma……明明是我很珍惜的人，我卻對她……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>無論你認為自己有什麼罪過，像現在這樣努力讓她繼續活下去也許是你唯一的贖罪方式。</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "唯一的贖罪方式嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>嗯，即使無法獲得原諒也要去做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "感覺主任你……也變了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我現在也擁有重視的人吧，像你一樣。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……對，我重視她……重視這個家，不想再看到任何人傷心了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "記憶格式化完畢。主任！目前為止都很順利！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>這些畫面是……這個女孩原本的記憶嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "是，這個階段會把容器的記憶格式化。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>她是個很美的女孩。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "是啊，但是……抱歉了。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteMemories_UI", "記憶刪除"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "……感覺……比想像中沈重……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>接下來就是你發揮的時候了。去吧，去救她。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma……這會有點痛，妳要忍耐一下……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "브리징 활성. 88%...89%...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 E"], "content": "동기화 완료. 접속 준비.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "정신 접속 개시.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 U"], "content": "정신 접속 개시.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "제발... 꼭 성공해야만 해...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "정신 접속... 성공! 해냈다!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "좋아!\n역시 문제없을 줄 알았다고!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 U"], "content": "「용기」안의 기억을 포맷합니다.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "주임님! 도움 주셔서 감사드립니다.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>...자네의 연구에도 매우 흥미가 있어서 말이야. 몇 년 못 본새에 나보다 더 주임 같아졌군.</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아직 멀었습니다... 지금은 가족을 구하는 일에만 몰두할 뿐인걸요. 주임님의 이상에 비하면...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>이상이라...\n난 천률을 어길만한 짓을 수도 없이 저질렀다.\n「외형 복제」와 같은 이 불결한 기술 역시 더 위로 올라가는 수단으로 사용했을 뿐이었지. 원래는 다시 사용하지 않으려던 기술이지만...</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그래도 수도 없이 간절히 부탁드렸던 제 마음을 알아주셔서 너무 감사드립니다...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>여자아이를 살리기 위한 네 집착이 내 마음을 조금 움직인 것일지도. 하지만 이건 다른 무고한 생명을 희생해야만 하는 일이라는 것을 기억해. 그리고 그 대가는...</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "네... 알고 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>자네... 정말 많이 변했군.</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n그렇습니까... 그런데 정말 똑같네요. 이 여자아이... 주임님의 지원으로 개조한 이후로는 본래 모습은 완전히 사라져버렸군요.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>네 아내는... 이 일을 받아들였나?</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "받아들일 겁니다. 전 꼭 성공해낼 거니까.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>그 사람의 외형과 기억을 갖는다고... 정말로 그 사람이 될 수 있다는 건가? 정말이지 인간의 존재 의의에 대한 근거는 실로 덧없는 것일 수도...</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>하지만 그렇기 때문에 더 소중함이 뭔지 알게 되는 것이겠지. 보편적인 도덕의 선을 과학으로 넘어서려 할 때, 자네 역시 큰 성장을 이루게 될 거야.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...전... 주임님이 말씀하신 것처럼 그렇게 대단하지 않습니다. Aroma는... 분명 제게 소중한 사람입니다. 전 그 아이를...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "자신이 무슨 죄를 지었던, 지금 이렇게 간절히 저 아이를 살리려는 노력이 네게는 유일한 속죄 방식일지도 모르지.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "유일한... 속죄...?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "그래. 설령 용서받지 못할 짓을 한다고 해도 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "감사합니다, 주임님... 변하셨군요.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "……나도 지금은... 지키고 싶은 소중한 사람이 있으니까. 너처럼 말이다.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "네... 그 아이도... 제 가족도... 다시는 소중한 사람이 다치는 모습을 보고 싶지 않습니다.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "기억 포맷 완료. 주임님! 현재까진 아무 이상 없습니다!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "이 화면은... 이 아이 본연의 기억인가?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그렇습니다. 지금 용기 안의 기억이 포맷되는 단계입니다.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "참 어여쁜 아이로군.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "네.\n...정말... 미안하다.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteMemories_UI", "기억 삭제"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 A"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 U"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["연구원 E"], "content": "생각했던 것보다... 마음이 무거워...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "이제 자네의 실력을 발휘할 때로군. 자, 가서 그 아이를 구해.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... 조금 아플 거야. 그래도 조금만 견뎌내줘....\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "橋接器啟動，88%……89%……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "界面同步完成，準備連線。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "開始精神連線。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "開始精神連線。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜託了……一定要成功……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "精神連線……成功！太好了！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好！我就知道一定沒問題！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "開始格式化「容器」記憶。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "主任，很感謝你的幫忙。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我對你的這個項目也很感興趣。幾年沒見，你真的變得比我還有主任的樣子了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我還差得遠呢……像現在這樣，也只是為了拯救自己的親人，跟你的理想比起來……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>理想……我做過太多傷天害理的事。「複製容貌」這種骯髒的技術，也是為了往上爬而不擇手段。原本已經被我封印了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜託你好多次，總算是答應了，真的很謝謝你……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你想拯救她的執著，讓我稍微有點共鳴了。不過記住了，這可是在犧牲了一條無辜的生命之下換來的，它的代價……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……我知道。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你……真的變了啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n但……還真的是一模一樣，這個女孩……在你的支援下被改造後，根本看不出她原本的樣子。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你老婆……會接受嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她會接受的，我會成功的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>有了一個人的容貌與記憶後，就能成為他嗎？人類的存在依據真的非常脆弱啊……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>但也正因如此才顯得珍貴。能為科學打破道德框架的你，也成長了不少。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……沒有主任說得那麼偉大。Aroma……明明是我很珍惜的人，我卻對她……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>無論你認為自己有什麼罪過，像現在這樣努力讓她繼續活下去也許是你唯一的贖罪方式。</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "唯一的贖罪方式嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>嗯，即使無法獲得原諒也要去做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "感覺主任你……也變了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我現在也擁有重視的人吧，像你一樣。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……對，我重視她……重視這個家，不想再看到任何人傷心了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "記憶格式化完畢。主任！目前為止都很順利！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>這些畫面是……這個女孩原本的記憶嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "是，這個階段會把容器的記憶格式化。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>她是個很美的女孩。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "是啊，但是……抱歉了。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DeleteMemories_UI", "記憶刪除"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 A"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 U"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究員 E"], "content": "……感覺……比想像中沈重……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>接下來就是你發揮的時候了。去吧，去救她。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma……這會有點痛，妳要忍耐一下……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "桥接器启动，88%……89%……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 E"], "content": "界面同步完成，准备连线。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "开始精神连线。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 U"], "content": "开始精神连线。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜托了……一定要成功……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "精神连线……成功！太好了！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "好！我就知道一定没问题！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 U"], "content": "开始格式化「容器」记忆。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "主任，很感谢你的帮忙。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我对你的这个项目也很感兴趣。几年没见，你真的变得比我还有主任的样子了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我还差得远呢……像现在这样，也只是为了拯救自己的亲人，跟你的理想比起来……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>理想……我做过太多伤天害理的事。 「复制容貌」这种肮脏的技术，也是为了往上爬而不择手段。原本已经被我封印了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "拜托你好多次，总算是答应了，真的很谢谢你……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你想拯救她的执着，让我稍微有点共鸣了。不过记住了，这可是在牺牲了一条无辜的生命之下换来的，它的代价……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嗯……我知道。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你……真的变了啊。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n但……还真的是一模一样，这个女孩……在你的支援下被改造后，根本看不出她原本的样子。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>你老婆……会接受吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "她会接受的，我会成功的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>有了一个人的容貌与记忆后，就能成为他吗？人类的存在依据真的非常脆弱啊……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>但也正因如此才显得珍贵。能为科学打破道德框架的你，也成长了不少。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……没有主任说得那么伟大。 Aroma……明明是我很珍惜的人，我却对她……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>无论你认为自己有什么罪过，像现在这样努力让她继续活下去也许是你唯一的赎罪方式。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "唯一的赎罪方式吗……？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>嗯，即使无法获得原谅也要去做。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "感觉主任你……也变了。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>……我现在也拥有重视的人吧，像你一样。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……对，我重视她……重视这个家，不想再看到任何人伤心了。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["研究员 A"], "content": "记忆格式化完毕。主任！目前为止都很顺利！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Phoenix]"], "content": "<i>这些画面是……这个女孩原本的记忆吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3301"], "content": 